history.content:
Hi everyone,

Tech + Social Impact is an organization that aims to create a tight-knit community in which members can explore, have candid conversations about, and take action on ways to use technology for social good.

Currently we are creating an app powered by ML to help people speak and communicate more effectively as well as exude more confidence. We have completed the basis for the UI and are looking for ML programmers who are interested in joining our team! For this summer & fall, we are looking for students who have programming experience and are willing to learn and collaborate.

Apply at https://forms.gle/dxq2tgXNjKDPCYYD8

If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the project lead Avi at Avnaryanchawla@gmail.com

Thanks!
